metadata.description: A moving origin story featuring a colorful cast of characters of all shapes, forms and species, each fighting for their place in society. The young Bigoodee embarks on Lady Rozenbilt’s extravagant seaplane where high society, criminals and monsters will mingle.  This voyage will forever change his life.  A complete story that takes place in the same universe as the critically acclaimed  District 14,  by award-winning authors Gabus and Reutimann.
metadata.name: The Fantastic Voyage of Lady Rozenbilt
